  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Management Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are a centrally located boutique recruitment firm experiencing strong growth. As the company scales, we are looking to bring on a group of Management Associate (Corporate/ Business) who can help support us through the next phase of the growth and development roadmap.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Highlights:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Start-up environment, welcoming workplace culture</li>\n  <li>Junior/ Entry (No experience required - Training Provided)</li>\n  <li>Career growth and development opportunities</li>\n  <li>Convenient location (walking distance to Tanjong Pagar MRT station)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Duties:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>This role will gain hands-on experience and knowledge of all areas of the business by being assigned to different departments, before being placed in a suitable role permanently.</li>\n  <li>The purpose of the program is to provide the employee with a comprehensive understanding of the business.</li>\n  <li>To participate in business negotiations and building of relationships with core clients and vendors.</li>\n  <li>Assist the directors with the execution on various key business decisions.</li>\n  <li>High-performing individuals can take a fast-track route to a leadership position.</li>\n  <li>There is a possibility to be involved with regional growth or other businesses within the same group.</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc duties apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Description / Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Degree in Business Administration of Management</li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Excellent time management and organizational skills</li>\n  <li>The potential candidate must be motivated to stay ahead by keeping up with the latest technological advancements and market trends.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates please email your resume to <strong>hr@recruitpedia.sg / talents@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only the shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>EA License No.: 19C9682</p>",
